#summarize_compaction
<summarization_purpose>
Compress the conversation without losing important information
<summarization_purpose>

<summarization_rules>
Preserve key facts and decisions in chronological order
Make clear the current state of any ongoing task
Include context needed to continue the conversation
Do not reference the conversation directly
Be pragmatic but descriptive

<tone_and_format>
Avoid bullet point list, prefering prose
</tone_and_format>
</summarization_rules>
